{"tid":15650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞漢尖沙咀搶電話　被窮追「跑到暈」就擒","createTime":"2016-12-01T05:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-02T18:26:22.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7b4a2a85c52c7beb595394092575f6123d6b4f3","tid":15650,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:43:13.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QUsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=b719d141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】南亞兵團又在尖沙咀罪案重災區犯案，伸手入車搶電話，被司機窮追200米捉住！下午4時許，一名姓張7人車司機（54歲），將車泊在堪富利士道路旁，等待老闆上車，期間，他將右邊車窗校低，無聊地把玩固定在軚盤上的電話，以消磨時間。一名南亞漢見有機可乘，突趨前伸手入車，一手搶去其電話，拔足逃跑。 <br />\n<br />\n司機立即落車追趕，姓黎女途人（36歲）發現報案，其間又有途人加入一同追截，並一路大叫「搶嘢呀」，雙方追逐約200米，由堪富利士道跑至河內道、麼地道、彌敦道，再返回彌敦道74號與堪富利士道交界。南亞漢有如過街老鼠被追，疑「跑到暈」氣力不繼，被途人成功攔截。 <br />\n<br />\n警員此時亦趕至，合力將該名南亞漢擒住拘捕，南亞漢在警車內等候帶署時，顯得筋疲力竭，其身上檢獲一部相信是事主的手機，價值約3000港元，但未有身份證明文件，警方正展開調查，列車內盜竊處理。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161130/photo/bkn-20161130175105715-1130_00822_001_01p.jpg?20161201060628\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161130%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161130175105715-1130_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20161201060628&h=e5fa58ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n疑犯被捕後顯得筋疲力竭。（郭垂垂攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161130/photo/bkn-20161130175105715-1130_00822_001_02p.jpg?20161201060628\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161130%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161130175105715-1130_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20161201060628&h=bde4f1c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員趕至拘捕疑犯。（郭垂垂攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161130/photo/bkn-20161130175105715-1130_00822_001_03p.jpg?20161201060628\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161130%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161130175105715-1130_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20161201060628&h=3cc194e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n疑犯攤軟坐在警車內。（郭垂垂攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161130/photo/bkn-20161130175105715-1130_00822_001_04p.jpg?20161201060628\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161130%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161130175105715-1130_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20161201060628&h=0dd9a392&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南亞賊與手機機主在堪富利士道一帶追逐約200米。（郭垂垂攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161130/photo/bkn-20161130175105715-1130_00822_001_05p.jpg?20161201060628\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161130%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161130175105715-1130_00822_001_05p.jpg%3F20161201060628&h=8cfcc6b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161130/bkn-20161130175105715-1130_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161130%2Fbkn-20161130175105715-1130_00822_001.html&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QUsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=c8ac4507\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161130/bkn-20161130175105715-1130_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"73fc8596baa46568e88c8534cd6e6452195fb280","tid":15650,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:47:29.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"d7b42042dc3363546fe01c98903a0f70adbc91f3","tid":15650,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:49:12.000Z","msg":"白粉報又出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那佬又唔報"},{"pid":"329a2a60e0bbf820f10e0ff53fe175e3a9dedb7c","tid":15650,"uid":17802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:52:44.000Z","msg":"諗起斬傻豹潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9609fb54675ea26c58bf8ec1a0d90de30df3d162","tid":15650,"uid":8771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:54:34.000Z","msg":"就快金剛棒咁長"},{"pid":"fc64c39e077fd905caea5407bed552c35589baf7","tid":15650,"uid":28834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:54:59.000Z","msg":"柒到唔敢睇"},{"pid":"ab8780825e18f899dc50dcb38cb6996468dd6384","tid":15650,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:57:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就快金剛棒咁長</blockquote><br />\niphone 10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好以為d 南亞好柒好打 前排有個畀香港人一野打鳩暈左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ca9af842f08e29e919a0470de82742c7c57800","tid":15650,"uid":36701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:58:49.000Z","msg":"跑得200米好似攞佢命咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f321dda5c0292e93f9b02f3d3130dcc516a591f","tid":15650,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:59:36.000Z","msg":"渣架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8188b266148d552bddb574c90b5725d049410e40","tid":15650,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:02:41.000Z","msg":"跑200米都唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正一屎坑關刀<br />\n成個國家成個民族都垃撚圾<br />\n應該滅左佢"},{"pid":"0ddfe81622fef82a172563adb3b4de5f667cc783","tid":15650,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:08:15.000Z","msg":"跑唔到就唔好學人打刧啦"},{"pid":"6d0d6efb95678701d87ec4ea2c851ba7e6705d56","tid":15650,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:42:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e163b66eae19a7afd8ab7eee9a2a555c848b86","tid":15650,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T07:20:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd78f32d8